</STRONG><FONT SIZE=2 color=#FFFFFF FACE=arial>
<P>Maybe we should make them fly too in case they have to go over water. Brief invulnerability if they are low on life and faster mana regeneration. Jeez I hope you are joking, but I will fall for your trap if it is. I am a spellcaster(necro). I have also used a wizard although just to newbie level 8. There are spells like Fade, Shadowstep, SoW, root, Darkness, and others which serve just fine for a get away. It is hard enough for a warrior to hit a strafing moving player as is. No way should casters be allowed to move and cast. Melee classes would be entirely useless.

